    RefIds:
    - rid: 693803550753423493
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 1a7bcfbb-e154-49d1-abac-ccae6fb46e1c
        Position: {x: 586, y: -394}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: The computer was meant to be my take on mutation, the theme.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423494
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 0e725733-429e-428e-b1b8-9aae366dd4bf
        Position: {x: 586, y: -667}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: The player gets a <i>Sequence</i>, something they must solve
          to get points, the points of course lead to greater mutation!
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423495
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 8da055c8-4f1b-437e-8b82-b2e9fc19370e
        Position: {x: 586, y: -935}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: The printer, which was the death of me to get working (It's not
          currently working). Is where these points showcase the mutation either
          through <b>Sparaxis</b> resistance, growth speed, or effectiveness.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423496
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: b42fff2d-00bf-4f3e-a74a-8b5a19b504e2
        Position: {x: 245, y: -935}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Eventually, the planet would become more green, and the Sparaxis
          plant infection would be lifted. More on Sparaxis in my world lore
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423497
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 1d4486ec-8b1e-4514-a4bc-5f9e95f77bcf
        Position: {x: 982, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: The Bialogical printer would print a plant seed based on your
          new genome, you could then grow and test it before sending it to earth
          to repopulate.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423498
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 4000a8aa-76ba-4314-a161-95f2d6a9ffad
        Position: {x: 1355, y: -68}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Pods of soil, varying in type based on earth, which you could
          grow your new seeds. I always pictures this like Stardew, but I never got
          around to it.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423499
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: d1edd06e-356f-46a5-91cc-ed3c9a1cfc78
        Position: {x: 1355, y: 195}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: The Shuttlle isn't for people, your on a one way trip to save
          earth of course!
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423500
      type: {class: EndNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: d285ca70-11fc-4ad8-a444-6f770c8a3e79
        Position: {x: 1404, y: 789}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423501
      type: {class: DialogOptionsNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: a0cdd2aa-f0a6-420c-b749-d47385ea76ef
        Position: {x: 682, y: 303}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: I'll let you choose, I reccoment the computer game! (Console
          found like this one) as it's pretty much the only thing working
        ResponseOptions:
        - Computer Info
        - Biological Printer
        - Gardens
        - Plant Shuttle Home
        - World Lore
        - Exit
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423502
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: a47d359e-5fd5-4851-a964-b74183c2cd6c
        Position: {x: 1724, y: 195}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Instead, it's to ship back ready products of seeds and plants
          to grow again. These are specalized pods that drop fast enough to dig into
          the gound, perfectly planting your new mutant plant.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423503
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 84a69975-4ebf-4461-aaad-e1a72995c22b
        Position: {x: 1371, y: 470}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: To keep it fairly short, in the far future a virus wipes out
          almost all living plants. This was known as the <b>Sparaxis</b> (which
          I named after a real <color=#FF58AC>flower</color>)
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423504
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: b51f5e81-fb62-44c3-bd40-d686e2051a01
        Position: {x: 1724, y: 502}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: 'With the last resources of earths civilization, they sent a
          lone researcher to develop resistant plant mutants away from the disease. '
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423505
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 319316d3-ed5b-4b79-8129-377c8d5b864a
        Position: {x: 2099, y: 502}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Game cycle would only have been about 30 minutes, each root gave
          extra percent and increased the world recovery rate. (like plague inc.
          lol)
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423506
      type: {class: StartNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 96225873-99a3-41b9-8c3f-e22c02af87cc
        Position: {x: -592, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423507
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: ac906ae5-b927-4e83-899b-357b6a3a3f02
        Position: {x: -122, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: First off, I did not finish it in time for the 36 hours. . .
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423508
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 279a6aec-e3ca-412c-aec6-a86510abc732
        Position: {x: -459, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Welcome to the <color=#EF32FF>Help Desk!</color> where I will
          explain some parts of the game.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 693803550753423509
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 961c1d51-3cb0-4cbe-8313-ee0a1d000022
        Position: {x: 230, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: However I learned a ton! I want to let you know what currently
          works and what doesnt, and my intentions that is at all interstings.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
